{"tid":866050,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過生存係為左D咩?","createTime":"2018-10-17T14:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T14:59:17.000Z","uid":121289,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f9643acafbd11b9cd56d2dc17711819ec041b64","tid":866050,"uid":121289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:29:18.000Z","msg":"做左廿幾年毒撚 <br />\n除左打工養老豆老母以外 我唔覺得自己有享受過生活<br />\n<br />\n但係自從遇到女神之後 我開始見到自己生存係有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我發誓要為左佢改變自己形象 咁先可以襯起佢同佢走埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n短短幾日 佢終於都攤左牌 <br />\n一直都係我一廂情願 由頭都尾佢都對我冇感覺<br />\n<br />\n喊完一輪 沖緊涼果陣一路係到諗<br />\n除左賺錢報答老豆老母之外 我仲有咩原因要生存係呢個世上?<br />\n我已經唔知點面對以後幾十年生活<br />\n可唔可以比我解脫?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係受夠啦"},{"pid":"59ad2dc607fe9f852b12a2994013cc36b535c011","tid":866050,"uid":146063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"你有冇一刻係開心過？"},{"pid":"61cc31569b1b4a6ecd3eec9ce2d974907054186e","tid":866050,"uid":164240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"轉gay<br />\n利申：非gay"},{"pid":"9624cda1900edf8e60c46ccc415e15a66945630d","tid":866050,"uid":121289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59ad2dc607fe9f852b12a2994013cc36b535c011","tid":866050,"uid":146063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"你有冇一刻係開心過？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:38:47.000Z","msg":"比你咁問法 諗諗下真係冇<br />\n我已經唔覺得呢個世界仲有事物會令到我開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca265fab5b62e1b5db4369fdaefd254b52b38ce9","tid":866050,"uid":146063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:39:33.000Z","msg":"你有冇中意做嘅野？"},{"pid":"ec2f49710ef568254f4bd2cd69e7da670de9c29e","tid":866050,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T14:40:49.000Z"